sentences: Seo Eun-kwang (Korean: 서은광; born November 22, 1990), also simply known as Eunkwang, is a South Korean singer, songwriter, entertainer, musical actor and the leader and main vocalist of the South Korean boy group BtoB.
Seo was born on November 22, 1990, in Yongin, Gyeonggi in South Korea.
section: == Biography ==

sentences: Seo reportedly began military duty by enlisting as an active duty soldier in the military band on August 21, 2018 at the ROK army's 27th division, nicknamed the 'We Will Win' unit in Gangwon-do's Hwacheon County.
section: == Biography == | === Military service ===

sentences: In October 2018, he received first place out of the recruits in the overall results during basic training.
section: == Biography == | === Military service ===

sentences: On March 14, he was selected as ROK-SWC for receiving more than 90 points in sit-ups, push-ups, 3 km running, 10 km full combat gear marching and more.
section: == Biography == | === Military service ===

sentences: He was discharged from the army on April 7, 2020.
